  <brief_title>Detection and/or Evaluation of Dense Breast Abnormalities Using Tomosynthesis and Digital Mammography</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Emerging Technology: Comparison of Breast Tomosynthesis and Digital Mammography in the Evaluation of Heterogeneously Dense and Extremely Dense Breasts</official_title>
  <sponsors>
